fields.description: The wait time to get a response from SharePoint Online. Default value is 5 minutes (00:05:00). Type: string (or Expression with resultType string), pattern: ((\d+)\.)?(\d\d):(60|([0-5][0-9])):(60|([0-5][0-9])).
fields.name: HTTPRequestTimeout

fields.description: The OData query to filter the data in SharePoint Online list. For example, "$top=1". Type: string (or Expression with resultType string).
fields.name: Query
